    "body": "### Expected\r\n`SAVE` button should be enabled for a new tag with valid content in all cases.\r\n\r\n### Observed\r\nAfter rotating from landscape mode to portrait, `SAVE` button will be disabled for a new tag:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/73365754/132836192-3b157382-ef3a-4434-bd7c-deead06fb5ea.mp4\r\n\r\n### Reproduced\r\n1. Open tags list\r\n2. Add a new tag, enter a valid name\r\n3. Make sure you get to landscape mode, then rotate back to portrait ~> `SAVE` button is disabled.\r\n\r\nDevice Model: Samsung A31\r\nAndroid Version: 10\r\nSimplenote Version: 2.21-rc-1\r\n",
